* Configuring Permissions
** Done in workspace UI
***_ Not Azure portal
***_ Sidebar > Compute > Permissions
** Add users or groups
***_ Search by name or email
***_ Set permission level
** Changes take effect immediately
***_ No cluster restart needed
** Use groups over individuals
***_ Simplifies management
***_ Add/remove via group membership
***_ Avoids manual cleanup
@endmindmap
